00:40:22.583 --> 00:40:24.416
ose e gjitha ishte nje budallallek.

00:40:24.708 --> 00:40:28.667
Por ndonjehere mund te jete ekstremisht, ekstremisht

00:40:29.583 --> 00:40:32.708
e veshtire ta ripershkruash mbrapsht;

00:40:32.959 --> 00:40:37.376
si semundjet, sic i quaj semundje te yuppies, (sindroma e lodhjes kronike),

00:40:37.583 --> 00:40:38.834
e cila tani eshte e pamundur

00:40:39.042 --> 00:40:40.834
sepse Hanuman ka hequr

00:40:41.042 --> 00:40:42.251
forcen elektromagnetike

00:40:42.416 --> 00:40:44.458
nga keta njerez dhe kjo s'funksionon,

00:40:44.708 --> 00:40:46.376
nuk lidhet me mendjen tuaj te ndergjegjshme.

00:40:46.583 --> 00:40:49.251
Pra mendja juaj e ndergjegjshme s'mund te veproje, vetem del.

00:40:49.667 --> 00:40:52.376
Vetem ata njerez, nese adhurojne Hanumana

00:40:52.667 --> 00:40:56.959
me te njejtin perkushtim, atehere mbase mund te shpetohen.

00:40:57.292 --> 00:40:59.959
