00:41:41.792 --> 00:41:45.416
ndonjehere ju zhvilloni keto rashes,

00:41:45.667 --> 00:41:48.376
pra nese ju vini gheru keto rashes korrigjohen.

00:41:48.583 --> 00:41:50.917
